Title: An Act Changing the Name of Nichols Air Base to Col. Jesus Villamor Air Base
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 166
An Act Changing the Name of Nichols Air Base to Col. Jesus Villamor Air Base
Section 1. Nichols Air Base shall hereafter be known and referred to as Col. Jesus Villamor Air Base.1Ã¢wphi1
